==Esperanto==
===Etymology===
Esperanto ''[[i-]]'' (indeterminate [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlative]] prefix) + ''[[-om]]'' (correlative ending of quantity)

===Correlative===
'''iom'''

# [[some]] of (indeterminate correlative of quantity)
#: Like other indeterminate correlatives, '''iom''' can be combined with ''[[ajn]]'', the adverbial particle of generality. '''''Iom''' ajn'' thus means ''any of''.

===Derived words===
*[[iomete]]
*[[iomege]]

